Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_query": "Proposing an improved Chain-of-Thought based on human thinking methods, evaluated purely through prompt tuning without fine-tuning or time-intensive experiments"
}

### Verification - Propose Policies (custom llm_mapping)

POST http://localhost:8000/airas/v1/verification/propose-policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_query": "Proposing an improved Chain-of-Thought based on human thinking methods, evaluated purely through prompt tuning without fine-tuning or time-intensive experiments",
    "llm_mapping": {
        "propose_verification_policy": {
            "llm_name": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6"
        }
