}

### Verification - Generate Method (default llm_mapping)

POST http://localhost:8000/airas/v1/verification/generate-method
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_query": "Proposing an improved Chain-of-Thought based on human thinking methods, evaluated purely through prompt tuning without fine-tuning or time-intensive experiments",
    "selected_policy": {
        "id": "0",
        "title": "Benchmark Comparison",
        "what_to_verify": "Whether the proposed human-aligned CoT template achieves higher accuracy than standard CoT on established benchmarks.",
        "method": "Evaluate on GSM8K and ARC-Challenge benchmarks using GPT-4o with the proposed template vs. standard CoT baseline.",
        "pros": ["Objective metric", "Reproducible"],
        "cons": ["Benchmark-specific", "May not generalize"]
    }
}

