    "llm_mapping": {
        "dispatch_experiment_code_generation": {
            "llm_name": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6"
        }
    }
}

### Verification - Get Experiment Code Status

GET http://localhost:8000/airas/v1/verification/experiment-code-status/auto-res2/my-experiment-repo/123456789
